cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA. 

The paper focuses on reinforcement learning in robotic manipulation and multi-agent tasks, which suggests it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The use of intrinsic motivation and exploration bias suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the emphasis on synergistic behavior and the proposed incentivization approach suggest it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
